@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_aejjio(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.sin(0.16) + (0.15 + (tmp + 0.53 * v0 + 0.78)))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.sin(v0))
    tmp = v0
    v0 = wp.sin(v2)
    v2 = (wp.abs(v1) * wp.exp(v1))
    data[tid] = v0
